<h3>Migrating old users</h3>

<p>Where you already using Vicancy before the widget got available? You might want to migrate all users over from
  their old (depreciated) videomanagers to their new homes. Here’s how this works:</p>
<ol>
  <li>We’ll send you a spreadsheet with all your clients that we have active in our system.</li>
  <li>Please look up the <code>client_id</code> for these clients in your database, and put them in the
    spreadsheet.
  </li>
  <li>We’ll update our database to mirror the spreadsheet. All clients will now be able to access their videos via
    the widget as well.
  </li>
</ol>

